OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,FAhead of the general election on July
OL,8,F4 we are looking at some of the big
OL,9,Fissues for people heading to the polls.
OL,11,FThe cost of living is affecting many
OL,12,Fpeople in the region, with high prices
OL,13,Fand stagnant wages leaving many
OL,14,Fhouseholds struggling.
OL,16,FWe spent some time with the Weston
OL,17,Ffamily in Newton Aycliffe, in County
OL,18,FDurham to see how they are coping.
