OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,FShopping smarter, using the car less
OL,8,Fand keeping a close eye on when the
OL,9,Fheating goes on are a few of the ways
OL,10,Fthe Weston family is trying to make
OL,11,Ftheir income go further.
OL,13,FEngineer Darran and charity volunteer
OL,14,FLisa live with their daughter, who is
OL,15,Fstudying for exams.
OL,17,FThey say the cost of running the
OL,18,Fhousehold has doubled.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
