OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,F"I think, like everyone else, food
OL,8,Fprices have gone through the roof,"
OL,9,Fsaid Darran. "Even things you use to
OL,10,Fmake a basic meal have more than
OL,11,Fdoubled.
OL,13,F"Fuel costs definitely for the car.
OL,14,FAnd years ago you could have the
OL,15,Fheating on for hours a day and not
OL,16,Fhave to worry about it. But literally
OL,17,Fall I hear when the heating goes on is
OL,18,Fmoney in a jar."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
