OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,FHe added: "If we went and spent #100
OL,8,Fat the shop, I would say we probably
OL,9,Fsay we get about a quarter as what we
OL,10,Fused to get maybe four years ago, five
OL,11,Fyears ago. And the prices aren't
OL,12,Fcoming down."
OL,14,FAs a family of animal lovers, they
OL,15,Fhave several rescue pets which also
OL,16,Fneed fed and cared for.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
