OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,FLisa said: "The dog food and the cat
OL,8,Ffood especially, I just don't
OL,9,Funderstand why they have to charge so
OL,10,Fmuch for them. But we do what we can.
OL,11,FWe love our animals and we can't let
OL,12,Fthem go without or anything. They're
OL,13,Four babies."
OL,15,FDarran says the family has cut back on
OL,16,Fcosts where possible, keeping the car
OL,17,Fat home to save on petrol and closely
OL,18,Fmonitoring gas and electric.
OL,20,FAnd they keep an eagle out for offers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
