OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,F"If there's a chicken and gravy pie
OL,8,Ffrom Tesco, for example, that are
OL,9,Fnormally four pound and it drops down
OL,10,Fto two, you can get two and it's like
OL,11,Fbuy one get one free," he added. "You
OL,12,Fcan have one for tea, for example, and
OL,13,Fyou can put one in the freezer for
OL,14,Flater. I think we've had to shop more
OL,15,Fsavvy now than we ever have done.
OL,16,FWe've had to make different choices on
OL,17,Fshampoos, go for own brand deodorants,
OL,18,Fthings like that.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
