OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,F"We'll only use the car now when we
OL,8,Fneed to. Fuel costs we were looking at
OL,9,Fnearly two pounds a litre. There's a
OL,10,Ffuel checker site you can go onto that
OL,11,Ftells you where the cheapest is in the
OL,12,Farea. I think I've run the car more on
OL,13,Fred lines than I have at any other
OL,14,Ftime."
OL,16,FThe last few years have taken more
OL,17,Fthan a financial tolls, says Lisa.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
