OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,F"It's definitely affecting our mental
OL,8,Fhealth," said Lisa. "When you're
OL,9,Ftrying to save up to have a day out
OL,10,Fand go somewhere it's hard because you
OL,11,Fhave to break into that money and we
OL,12,Fhave to use it to pay for something
OL,13,Felse. It is really hard but you have
OL,14,Fto manage on what you've got
OL,15,Fbasically."
OL,17,FWhen they think of the future it isn't
OL,18,Fthemselves they have in mind.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
