OL,3,C'Our running costs have doubled' - how
OL,4,Cthis family copes with the cost of
OL,5,Cliving
OL,7,FDarran said: "I'd like to think that
OL,8,Fmy youngest daughter who goes to
OL,9,Fcollege this year has something of a
OL,10,Fbetter future. But will she able to
OL,11,Fafford a house? Because she'll be
OL,12,Ftaxed to death the moment she starts
OL,13,Fearning. House prices are going
OL,14,Fridiculously high. The cost of running
OL,15,Fthem. I fear how she's going to
OL,16,Fmanage."
OL,18,FTheir main hope, after election,
OL,19,Fwhoever is in charge, is that families
OL,20,Fbudgets go further.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
